{"tid":1252171,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《007》導演傳聞沉迷Red Dead Redemption 2 拖慢拍攝進度","createTime":"2019-06-23T00:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T02:18:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5f33ee7cb69eeb3cb59d79b9646fd884a782c1","tid":1252171,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"第25部《007》電影從宣布籌拍至今，一直都多災多難，先是導演換人，再到男主角丹尼爾克雷格（Daniel Craig）腳受傷，拍攝進度被迫一延再延，日前又爆出導演凱瑞福永（Cary Joji Fukunaga）因為打遊戲遲到，事後要求全劇組一起加班，但有部分人不同意，再度拖慢了拍攝進度。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《太陽報》報導，有爆料人士稱日前為了打遊戲，遲到3個小時，因此要求全劇組周末加班，追上落後進度，對此有不少工作人員都非常不滿，大部分人都拒絕在周末加班，也不願意為了工作而放棄父親節，因劇組內部人不滿他的作為，決定跳出向媒體爆料。<br />\n<br />\n對此，凱瑞福永19日隨即在IG上澄清，他曬出一張前輩Mark Tildesley的照片，並稱自己從對方的身上學到了許多，包括如何當一位導演，稱在拍攝過程中，每分每秒都是按照計劃行事，所有都事情都是按照時間表再進行，雖然很辛苦，但他依舊認為這份工作是全世界最好的工作，「我永遠不會不尊重那些辛苦工作的演員及工作人員，我們大家是一體的。」<br />\n<br />\n凱瑞福永承認自己愛打遊戲，但是他目前所玩的《碧血狂殺2》，玩了好幾個月，至今進度仍是63％，強調自己並未因為遊戲而耽誤工作，還笑言：「在我拍攝《Bond 25》結束前，也請大家不要向我爆雷任何關於遊戲的結局，不然我一定會很火大。」幽默回應拖慢拍攝進度一事。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190620/1471966.htm#ixzz5rcwg0IJ6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190620%2F1471966.htm%23ixzz5rcwg0IJ6&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=b5e53b1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190620/1471966.htm#ixzz5rcwg0IJ6</a>"},{"pid":"ed32bc9fca36a0011901d1b04f975a34f3f50171","tid":1252171,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:46:15.000Z","msg":"咁就仆街喇"},{"pid":"3ad03496798135f7cd4f832d1f97555d231dd280","tid":1252171,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"屄血狂撒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289fd83499e302c19fed5590a5b9b024ee21c54f","tid":1252171,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:53:24.000Z","msg":"打機打到不能自拔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ad3657d3ed3a9fcfb320c606b823e6c9151f51","tid":1252171,"uid":36167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"太陽報最鐘意作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0698200217fa7627889151d4b70a588d65e5f154","tid":1252171,"uid":261098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:17:32.000Z","msg":"比成隊crew屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d272344f3ce055b5d5f2de4004afc3e69f1f8a9a","tid":1252171,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4ad3657d3ed3a9fcfb320c606b823e6c9151f51","tid":1252171,"uid":36167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"太陽報最鐘意作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"Page3😍"}]}